				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=210230&amp;sid=17c5de6da12757c60666e1609ffd8ddf#210230"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Wed Aug 11, 2004 4:07 am<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: OT: Condoms, the Pill and Abortion, the moral difference</span></td>
			        <td valign="top" align="right" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="ignore.php?mode=add&amp;username=Wreak Havvoc&amp;topic=16370&amp;sid=17c5de6da12757c60666e1609ffd8ddf"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_ignore.gif" alt="Add User to Ignore List" title="Add User to Ignore List" border="0" /></a> <a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=210230&amp;sid=17c5de6da12757c60666e1609ffd8ddf"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
